      <p></p>
<p>The loss of a friend is devastating. These messages offer support and understanding to friends during their time of grief, focusing on friendship and shared memories.</p>
<li>I was so saddened to hear about the loss of your friend.</li>
<li>My heart goes out to you during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending you my love and support.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry for your loss; your friend will be dearly missed.</li>
<li>Cherishing the memories we shared with your friend.</li>
<li>Remember the good times, and let those memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Your friend's spirit will live on in our hearts.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you navigate your grief.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, always, if you need a friend to lean on.</li>
<li>Your friend was a special person, and they will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>May your memories of your friend bring you peace and solace.</li>
<li>Holding you in my thoughts and sending all my love.</li>
<li>Let me know if there's anything I can do to support you.</li>
