<li>May you find peace and comfort in the days ahead.</li>
    

      <h2 id="expressions-of-care-and-support">Expressions of Care and Support</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>Practical support is often as valuable as words during times of grief.  These messages offer both, showing that you're there to help in tangible ways.</p>
