<li>I'm here to help in any way I can – with errands, meals, or just listening.</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you. Please accept my heartfelt condolences.</li>
<li>Please let me know how I can help ease your burden during this time.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and courage. I'm here to support you.</li>
<li>Don't hesitate to call on me for anything at all, big or small.</li>
<li>Thinking of you, and sending love and practical support.</li>
